SENATE BILL DRS35118-LG-107
Short Title: Tamil Pongal State Holiday. (Public)
Sponsors: Senator Mohammed (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO ESTABLISH JANUARY FOURTEENTH OF EACH YEAR AS TAMIL
3 PONGAL DAY IN NORTH CAROLINA.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. Chapter 103 of the General Statutes is amended by adding a new
6 section to read:
7 "§ 103-19. Tamil Pongal Day.
8 The fourteenth day of January of each year is designated as Tamil Pongal Day in North
9 Carolina."
10 SECTION 2. This act is effective when it becomes law.
*DRS35118-LG-107*

